Pong Game.

On Screen:
1. Score - two scores 
2. Divider on screen - two sides
3. Ball
4. Paddles


Steps:
1. Create the screen
2. Create and move the paddles
3. Create the ball and make it move across the screen
4. Detect collision with the wall and bounce
5. Detect collision with the paddles
6. Detect when paddle misses
7. Keep score 